    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Generally, a class of hydrocarbons found  in the volatile oils of plants, especially the coniferous and aurantiaceous orders. Most  common is the chief constituent of turpentine, pinene.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
